Project description

iCalEvents

Simple Python 3 library to download, parse and query iCal sources.

Build info

last push:

master:

Documentation

https://icalevents.readthedocs.io/en/latest/

Usage

iCloud:

from icalevents.icalevents import eventses  = events(<iCloud URL>, fix_apple=True)

Google:

from icalevents.icalevents import eventses  = events(<Google Calendar URL>)

Contributing

You will need poetry and pre-commit installed and than run.

pre-commit install

Happy contributing!
